truct, template strings), 好似搞到複雜咗! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ncode: <a href=\"https://paste.ofcode.org/ujCSnuDztQRvJHzw6Zxmu6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaste.ofcode.org%2FujCSnuDztQRvJHzw6Zxmu6&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZTzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0936bfd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://paste.ofcode.org/ujCSnuDztQRvJHzw6Zxmu6</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/040626_79259735705a3e78432f6c9935a1568f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F04%2F040626_79259735705a3e78432f6c9935a1568f.jpg&h=b41e0433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/040658_8b5036ba79f63ab9f74ef4e51344c736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F04%2F040658_8b5036ba79f63ab9f74ef4e51344c736.jpg&h=60124050&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2700dcb2d25f40169472c905333abf4dc96c162e","tid":184064,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T20:38:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉, 瞓唔著, 順便做埋refactoring同加多啲ES6嘢(i.e. for-in construct, template strings), 好似搞到複雜咗! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ncode: <a href=\"https://paste.ofcode.org/ujCSnuDztQRvJHzw6Zxmu6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaste.ofcode.org%2FujCSnuDztQRvJHzw6Zxmu6&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZTzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0936bfd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://paste.ofcode.org/ujCSnuDztQRvJHzw6Zxmu6</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/040626_79259735705a3e78432f6c9935a1568f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F04%2F040626_79259735705a3e78432f6c9935a1568f.jpg&h=b41e0433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/040658_8b5036ba79f63ab9f74ef4e51344c736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F04%2F040658_8b5036ba79f63ab9f74ef4e51344c736.jpg&h=60124050&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌, 原來有bug, 要改line#25為:<br />\nconsole.log(<code>${arrayKey} Fibonacci numbers [green]${array[arrayKey][0]}[/green] to ${n} are:</code>);<br />\n咁output header for Modern Fibonacci先會啱番:<br />\nModern Fibonacci numbers <span style=\"color: green;\">0</span> to 10 are:"},{"pid":"5b05ed83453984cd37015756bd03b466ff143dfc","tid":184064,"uid":69481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:33:22.000Z","msg":"ES6 應該點樣開始學, 齊睇過同ES5 對比唔入腦"},{"pid":"12936d26ce7d3dd79df6790a4fb578fd18bf7c86","tid":184064,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:44:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉, 瞓唔著, 順便做埋refactoring同加多啲ES6嘢(i.e. for-in construct, template strings), 好似搞到複雜咗! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ncode: <a href=\"https://paste.ofcode.org/ujCSnuDztQRvJHzw6Zxmu6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaste.ofcode.org%2FujCSnuDztQRvJHzw6Zxmu6&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZTzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0936bfd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://paste.ofcode.org/ujCSnuDztQRvJHzw6Zxmu6</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/040626_79259735705a3e78432f6c9935a1568f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F04%2F040626_79259735705a3e78432f6c9935a1568f.jpg&h=b41e0433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/040658_8b5036ba79f63ab9f74ef4e51344c736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F04%2F040658_8b5036ba79f63ab9f74ef4e51344c736.jpg&h=60124050&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\njohn linux未"},{"pid":"a41292338ba928b900b36736613aa93849042836","tid":184064,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T11:22:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ES6 應該點樣開始學, 齊睇過同ES5 對比唔入腦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不如你先搞熟vanilla JS嘅<span style=\"color: green;\">basic syntax</span>(e.g. methods vs functions vs constructors, IIFE, hoisting, nesting, closures), <span style=\"color: green;\">data types</span>(e.g. null vs undefined), <span style=\"color: green;\">built-in objects</span>(e.g.Object, Array, String, Math等)<span style=\"color: green;\">嘅常用methods</span>, <span style=\"color: green;\">object literals</span>(vs JSON), <span style=\"color: green;\">prototypal inheritance</span>(vs classical object-oriented inheritance), browser's <span style=\"color: green;\">DOM</span> objects &amp; DOM manipulation等等,  再去google and study下<span style=\"color: green;\">一大堆vanilla JS嘅weaknesses</span>, 先至去學ES6, 因為<ins>大部分ES6/ES6+ features唔係一堆syntax sugar of vanilla JS(and ECMAScripts up to ES5), 就係一堆針對vanilla JS weaknesses而發展出嚟嘅物體! </ins><br />\n<br />\ni.e. 你要好了解一大堆pre-ES6 features/weaknesses先會對ES6/ES6+嘅印象深刻啲! <br />\n(P.S. 不過有啲ES6/ES6+ features唔太關vanilla JS事, e.g. promise constructor, async method, await operator, 呢啲其實係關Node.js事, 所以你要熟埋Node.js!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"b93bc76d769777f0567a33ff6be5e88bf7f2f098","tid":184064,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T11:33:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唉, 瞓唔著, 順便做埋refactoring同加多啲ES6嘢(i.e. for-in construct, template strings), 好似搞到複雜咗! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ncode: <a href=\"https://paste.ofcode.org/ujCSnuDztQRvJHzw6Zxmu6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaste.ofcode.org%2FujCSnuDztQRvJHzw6Zxmu6&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZTzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0936bfd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://paste.ofcode.org/ujCSnuDztQRvJHzw6Zxmu6</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/040626_79259735705a3e78432f6c9935a1568f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F04%2F040626_79259735705a3e78432f6c9935a1568f.jpg&h=b41e0433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/040658_8b5036ba79f63ab9f74ef4e51344c736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F04%2F040658_8b5036ba79f63ab9f74ef4e51344c736.jpg&h=60124050&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\njohn linux未</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌, 我XP裏面有裝<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>speedLinux</strong></span>(based on coLinux, and powered by Ubuntu 12.04 LTS)架, 係Linux度我有install到Node version 6, support 9X%嘅ES6, 唔駛另外用babel-node咁煩!<br />\n(XP本身只support到Node version 4, 要玩ES6/ES6+ features, 要另外用babel-node先得, 唉! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"dd9db65c57b0ba6ba8fd1add9d7b0a3fc294565a","tid":184064,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T11:39:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唉, 瞓唔著, 順便做埋refactoring同加多啲ES6嘢(i.e. for-in construct, template strings), 好似搞到複雜咗! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ncode: <a href=\"https://paste.ofcode.org/ujCSnuDztQRvJHzw6Zxmu6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaste.ofcode.org%2FujCSnuDztQRvJHzw6Zxmu6&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZTzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0936bfd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://paste.ofcode.org/ujCSnuDztQRvJHzw6Zxmu6</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/040626_79259735705a3e78432f6c9935a1568f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F04%2F040626_79259735705a3e78432f6c9935a1568f.jpg&h=b41e0433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/040658_8b5036ba79f63ab9f74ef4e51344c736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F04%2F040658_8b5036ba79f63ab9f74ef4e51344c736.jpg&h=60124050&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\njohn linux未</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌, 我XP裏面有裝<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>speedLinux</strong></span>(based on coLinux, and powered by Ubuntu 12.04 LTS)架, 係Linux度我有install到Node version 6, support 9X%嘅ES6, 唔駛另外用babel-node咁煩!<br />\n(XP本身只support到Node version 4, 要玩ES6/ES6+ features, 要另外用babel-node先得, 唉! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\npeasantry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed944114cafa949184301b3a547d31ac15debc0a","tid":184064,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T11:59:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n......<br />\n屌, 我XP裏面有裝<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>speedLinux</strong></span>(based on coLinux, and powered by Ubuntu 12.04 LTS)架, 係Linux度我有install到Node version 6, support 9X%嘅ES6, 唔駛另外用babel-node咁煩!<br />\n(XP本身只support到Node version 4, 要玩ES6/ES6+ features, 要另外用babel-node先得, 唉! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\npeasantry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係點? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b831f4fd7350ebc38fc8da274b8a15ddadfd9d","tid":184064,"uid":79869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:14:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ES6 應該點樣開始學, 齊睇過同ES5 對比唔入腦</blockquote><br />\n個人推薦當JAVA咁寫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n應該係最快接受到ES6既方式<br />\n<a href=\"http://tomasalabes.me/blog/_site/web-development/2015/09/16/ES6-Classes-For-Java-Developers.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftomasalabes.me%2Fblog%2F_site%2Fweb-development%2F2015%2F09%2F16%2FES6-Classes-For-Java-Developers.html&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZTzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b2fded97\" target=\"_blank\">http://tomasalabes.me/blog/_site/web-development/2015/09/16/ES6-Classes-For-Java-Developers.html</a><br />\n<br />\nbtw, 要了解ES6就要先了解ES5既伏位....你就會明ES6有幾偉大<br />\n但要了解ES5既伏位可能需要花一點腦汁去睇example同syntax rule <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33399126145cb8ed9d44ccb25ccf4e026a0eccf6","tid":184064,"uid":79869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:18:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>(P.S. 不過有啲ES6/ES6+ features唔太關vanilla JS事, e.g. promise constructor, async method, await operator, 呢啲其實係關Node.js事, 所以你要熟埋Node.js!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實Node.js都係follow ES6 而已...只係生態上有能力比browser早implement<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw, async/await 唔算ES6, 剛開始接獨ES6既人可以跳過"}]}